metadata.name: Breakfast is served!
metadata.description: Breakfast is served! It's a captivating collaboration between talented artists @lookitookapic (aka @ksyuzzi) and @serc1n for the prestigious NUDE X GM World exhibition. This striking photo is a part of my "The Bunny Garden" project, where I skillfully capture the beauty and uniqueness of my models through playful, sparkling, and delightfully crazy erotic nude shoots
